description: PlasmaTech, Inc., a development stage company, designs, markets, and sells illuminated signboard products using plasma lighting technology. The plasma lighting technology enables the reproduction of illuminated photo-quality images onto thin plastic. The company intends to market its technology to the trade show industry; and focus on signage applications in industrial trade show exhibits and displays, such as illuminated banners and wall displays. PlasmaTech, Inc. was founded in 2004 and is based in Atlanta, Georgia.
